{"tid":1767421,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"環球時報︰或會發布「不可靠實體清單」 報復美國眾議院通過《維吾爾人權政策法案》","createTime":"2019-12-03T09:56:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-03T12:57:20.000Z","uid":212626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"6699f617ce272ebc5ec6cb7acc217526267df4a5","tid":1767421,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T09:56:42.000Z","msg":"《環球時報》於Twitter引述未注明消息來源的帖文稱，針對美國眾議院即將通過的新疆相關法案，中國可能採取報復措施，當中可能包括發布「不可靠實體清單」。<br />\n<br />\n帖文引述，預計美國眾議院將通過一項與新疆有關的法案，美國的新疆相關法案將損害中國企業利益，促使中國「加快」行動。中國將發布「不可靠實體清單」，其中包括美國實體，環球時報帖文指，中國可能採取報復措施，其中可能包括限制美國相關人員及公司進入中國的黑名單，包括共和黨參議員Marco Rubio在內的美國政界人士，可能亦會受到制裁。<br />\n<br />\n美國參議院9月通過《維吾爾人權政策法案》（Uyghur Human Rights Policy Act），呼籲美國政府就新疆問題加大對華施壓，密切監督大批維吾爾人被關押在「再教育營」的情況，並考慮對負有責任的官員施予制裁。<br />\n<a href=\"https://inews.hket.com/article/2511372/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finews.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2511372%2F&d=QAb612WS2prazXX2mE0KscjT01h1KCp2%2Bw2KB0oDRGE%3D&h=0d629720\" target=\"_blank\">https://inews.hket.com/article/2511372/</a>"},{"pid":"404f5065f615777169b3966e698a7ae17924d9b9","tid":1767421,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:14:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52ce5f2dcec0ffd5f74838996c700c4ddb507f24","tid":1767421,"uid":221490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-03T10:18:13.000Z","msg":"制裁APPLE先啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/nosee.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6efcbea7a6ce48d7f315570f7f544c18f